      "writtenOn": "2020-08-06T15:17:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "That\u0027s fair to me; I think Mike\u0027s plan would work, but I support adding it later. Perhaps when we land in an SkEffect world, those requirements will be the preconditions for doing a CPU-level evaluation instead of it being tied to \"shader vs. color filter\"",
